  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9f\u0bc0\u0b9a\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A man was arrested for hoarding diesel and selling it at a high price in Yali",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna. Thellipappa police have arrested a man who was selling diesel at a high price by storing it in a measuring stick.",
        "Based on the information received by the police that diesel was being stored and sold in a shop in the area under the Tellipapa police division, the police conducted raids.",
        "During this, 291 liters of diesel and equipment used for sale were seized by the police and the police also arrested the 42-year-old shop owner on the charge of hoarding the diesel."
      ],
